reviews.review_text:
Sounds Nice...always like FOB Senn441s Hey All-

Not the best GD show I saw, not by a long shot, but still an enjoyable way to spend a warm Saturday night in April an hour south of UCLA (my alma mater).  Very nice sounding; will post if I find any anomalies when I've heard the whole gig.

Three stars for the performance.  
Four+ stars for the recording.

Eric
Not Bad Highlights:  Surprisingly fast Eyes Of The World for 86
